        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class='tip success'><p>持續更新中<p></div><hr><h1 id="主題-Butterfly"><a href="#主題-Butterfly" class="headerlink" title="主題 Butterfly"></a>主題 Butterfly</h1><p>提示 ：以下為 Butterfly 作者 Jerry 提供的文章，按照個人需求設置</p><h2 id="主題安裝-Butterfly"><a href="#主題安裝-Butterfly" class="headerlink" title="主題安裝 Butterfly"></a>主題安裝 Butterfly</h2><ul><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/21cfbf15/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(一) 快速開始</a></li></ul><h2 id="主題設置-Butterfly"><a href="#主題設置-Butterfly" class="headerlink" title="主題設置 Butterfly"></a>主題設置 Butterfly</h2><ul><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/dc584b87/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(二) 主題頁面</a></li><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/4aa8abbe/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(三) 主題配置-1</a></li><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/ceeb73f/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(四) 主題配置-2</a></li><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/98d20436/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(五) 主題問答</a></li><li><a href="https://demo.jerryc.me/posts/4073eda/">Butterfly 安裝文檔(六) 進階教程</a></li></ul><h1 id="主題美化-Butterfly-持續更新"><a href="#主題美化-Butterfly-持續更新" class="headerlink" title="主題美化 Butterfly (持續更新)"></a>主題美化 Butterfly (持續更新)</h1><h2 id="推薦文章"><a href="#推薦文章" class="headerlink" title="推薦文章"></a>推薦文章</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.antmoe.com/posts/a811d614/index.html">小康博客 - Hexo博客之butterfly主题优雅魔改系列（持续更新）</a></li><li><a href="http://home.ustc.edu.cn/~pscgylotti/blogs/2020/05/09/butterfly/">Pscgylotti’s Blog - 如果你使用了butterfly做hexo主题</a></li><li><a href="https://akilar.top/posts/f99b208/">Akilar - 基于 Butterfly 主题的美化日记</a></li><li><a href="https://butterfly.lete114.top/article/Butterfly-config.html">Lete 乐特 - Butterfly主题美化-无修改源码 (持续更新中…)</a></li></ul><h2 id="美化記錄"><a href="#美化記錄" class="headerlink" title="美化記錄"></a>美化記錄</h2><div class='tip' ><p>注意 ：以下為個人美化主題記錄，Butterfly版本 ：3.7.1<p></div><h3 id="Menu-Item-彩色選單"><a href="#Menu-Item-彩色選單" class="headerlink" title="Menu Item 彩色選單"></a>Menu Item 彩色選單</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* Menu Item 彩色選單 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* .Icon:before&#123;color:Hex Color&#125; */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.fa-home</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>&#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#ff5656</span>;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.fa-archive</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>&#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#fa9747</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.fa-tags</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>&#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#fadc49</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.fa-folder-open</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>&#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#47fb74</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.fa-book-open</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>&#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#506bff</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.fa-heart</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:before</span>&#123;<span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#ff5ce4</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Site-Name-amp-Subtitle-螢光標題"><a href="#Site-Name-amp-Subtitle-螢光標題" class="headerlink" title="Site Name &amp; Subtitle 螢光標題"></a>Site Name &amp; Subtitle 螢光標題</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span>